Module com.example.javaproject1
Package controller

Class AddPartMenu

java.lang.Object
controller.AddPartMenu
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class AddPartMenu extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
This is the controller class that deals with logic surrounding the add Part section of the inventory tool RUNTIME ERROR: a runtime error occurs if not all text fields are populated, the system will not save and process the addition of a part as needed. This was fixed by implementing code that provided errors, in the form of popups, if the wrong information or no information was provided at all.
